---
title: Honey Halloumi, Chicken & Fattoush Salad with Radish & Garlic Dip
description: This salad sensation will take you on a culinary adventure straight to the heart of the Middle East! Crunchy veggies, crispy tortilla chips and golden halloumi kissed by a drizzle of sticky honey all come together for a fresh and flavourful meal.

